expression = re.compile(rfc._TOKEN_REGEX)
invalid_tokens = [chr(127)] + [chr(x) for x in range(0, 32)]
invalid_tokens += ['(', ')', '<', '>', '@', ',', ';', ':', '\\', '"', '/',
    '[', ']', '?', '=', '{', '}', ' ', '\t']
for invalid_token in invalid_tokens:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch('abc' + invalid_token +
        'def')), msg="Invalid Token 'abc{t}def' was not flagged".format(t=
        invalid_token))
